subject: meta-fii/meta-kudo: Add Ampere Altra SMpro hwmon driver
commitMessage:
meta-fii/meta-kudo: Add Ampere Altra SMpro hwmon driver

Using this patch before it merge into the openBMC linux
upstream. It provides three types of monitor
1. SMpro hwmon dirver
2. SMpro misc dirver
3. SMpro RAS report driver

Tested-by:
1. Load image on the Nuvoton RunBMC CRB
2. Use ipmitool to test the command under BMC console
  a. ipmitool mc info
  b. ipmitool sdr
  c. ipmitool lan print
  d. ipmitool channel info 1
  e. ipmitool user list 1
  f. ipmitool chassis status
  g. ipmitool raw 0x06 0x01
  h. ipmitool power status

Signed-off-by: Lancelot Kao <lancelot.kao@fii-usa.com>
Change-Id: Ia9b193de2d9634dfc10b024ca80ec9d06bd942aa
